# Component Guidelines

1. Use the article-content class for rendering HTML content safely
2. Always use Next.js Link for navigation, not the Lucide React Link icon
3. Maintain consistent styling with Tailwind utility classes
4. Use dangerouslySetInnerHTML only with proper content sanitization

## Examples

- Article content rendering: [daily-comment-section.tsx](mdc:components/sections/daily-comment-section.tsx)
  - Uses dangerouslySetInnerHTML with the article-content class
  - Properly uses Next.js Link component for navigation

## CSS Guidelines

- Global styles in [globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css)
- Component-specific styles should use Tailwind utility classes
- The article-content class provides styling for HTML content